text: Mötzingen is a municipality in Böblingen in Baden-Württemberg, Germany. == Mayor == Since February 2008, Marcel Hagenlocher is the mayor of Mötzingen. He is the successor of Thomas Sprißler (born 1966), a mayor of Mötzingen from 1994 to 2008. == References == Category:Böblingen (district)
